PS C:\> $NewSuffix = "-prod A"
PS C:\> Get-HPOVNetwork -type Ethernet | % { Set-HPOVNetwork -network $_ -Name ($_.name + $NewSuffix) }
Get all Ethernet networks, and add a new Suffix to their names.
